{"tid":496790,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"羅渣士：當年幾乎執教曼城","createTime":"2017-12-12T05:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T10:36:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"20a272ff5ee2011c53c0bfc25db1d60dd012410d","tid":496790,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Yt7A02elDoz4Cy37BAznhy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=7410c4ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】現任些路迪領隊羅渣士透露，2009年曾有機會加入文仙尼的曼城助教團，但由突然獲得史雲斯聘請為領隊，最終放棄投效曼城。<br />\n<br />\n歐霸盃32強周一完成抽籤，當大眾都將目光放在英超勁旅阿仙奴及西甲、德甲等黑馬的賽序時，兩位曾經執教英超勁旅的教頭被抽中在歐霸對碰的戲碼，就被人忽視了。前利物浦領隊羅渣士（Brendan Rodgers）帶領的蘇超班霸些路迪，將與俄超球隊辛尼特爭奪16強席位，而辛尼特的主帥，正是曾帶領曼城贏得英超冠軍的文仙尼（Roberto Mancini）。<br />\n<br />\n抽籤結果出爐後，羅渣士自揭與文仙尼相當有淵源，兩人曾經幾乎成為同事：「那時我與曼城討論，回去擔任一隊教練的可能性&mdash;&mdash;雷丁解除了我的領隊職務，而我當時想，我應該沒有機會得到領隊工作。我與曼城傾談，一切都很順利，我更飛到米蘭與文仙尼會面。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，事情如何發展，大家都一清二楚。羅渣士最終未有成為文仙尼的副手，而是接受史雲斯的邀請，執教這支威爾斯球隊，更領軍於2011年升上英超。羅渣士本人可能對此感到可惜，但網民們就相當「毒舌」。在《BBC》報道的留言欄裡，有人留言道：「幸好他沒有這樣做。」更有人表示：「為他感到難過。他完全不清楚事實：在利物浦時有蘇亞雷斯，很幸運，而現在執些路迪......那已經說明了一切。」"},{"pid":"918acd9f095c35f8ec35fa19aaa5ed92d71c0a9d","tid":496790,"uid":29993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"渣sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18311a764561a2f6da17bf1eb99089d9ac016a89","tid":496790,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"去左曼城就有英超了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利物浦欠渣土一個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f7ac56d5d0d4c69f50f99b600f4e5c8701bf25","tid":496790,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更有人表示：「為他感到難過。他完全不清楚事實：在利物浦時有蘇亞雷斯，很幸運，而現在執些路迪......那已經說明了一切。」</blockquote><br />\n死痢狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89c7dc9f62be88deba4a35b17f8cddfae7ecbab","tid":496790,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>更有人表示：「為他感到難過。他完全不清楚事實：在利物浦時有蘇亞雷斯，很幸運，而現在執些路迪......那已經說明了一切。」</blockquote><br />\n死痢狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知佢想表達乜"},{"pid":"233a80ed6cd09e8e27073855a54220aac19cd2ab","tid":496790,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"有羅渣曼城一早拎到歐聯"},{"pid":"8d86c82fd86a512066386766d10ca452dac857a8","tid":496790,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>更有人表示：「為他感到難過。他完全不清楚事實：在利物浦時有蘇亞雷斯，很幸運，而現在執些路迪......那已經說明了一切。」</blockquote><br />\n死痢狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知佢想表達乜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明自己有料做山寨王<br />\n一出到歐聯就做肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8731e00ec12af733e4db49de3bf85568538961f","tid":496790,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"羅渣你是我最想留住的幸運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}